    "arguments": {
      "note_id": "1764731543071"
    }
  },
  "result": "Note(1764731543071, Front='What is H\u2082O?', Back='Water (the chemical formula for water)', tags=['chem&lt;TRUNCATED&gt;"
}

All working! Here’s what happened:

Added a card with Front=“What is H₂O?” and Back=“Water”
Updated the back to “Water (the chemical formula for water)” and added the tag “chemistry”
Verified with get_note — the changes persisted

The note ID is 1764731543071. What would you like to test next?
Try the various find ones that we haven’t done yet.


